ork automation<br>\u2022 Integration with other systems<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"3-find-the-best-software-development-company\"><\/span>3. Find the Best Software Development Company<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Several custom software development companies exist in the market. Therefore choosing the best company may be challenging, especially if you are a small or new business. Identifying the right company to develop the best software requires research.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Any company may not understand the needs of your business. Outsourcing is common as it comes with several benefits. A <a href=\"https:\/\/www.statista.com\/statistics\/189788\/global-outsourcing-market-size\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">recent study<\/a> showed that the outsourcing market reached USD 92.5 billion by 2019. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Some of the major benefits of outsourcing include:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u2022 It saves time<br>\u2022 It ensures the development of quality software without any risks<br>\u2022 It makes the scaling process easy<br>\u2022 These companies have qualified technicians to develop the software<br>\u2022 It provides access to several services<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Some of the things to consider when choosing a software development company include:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u2022 Level of experience<br>\u2022 Customer reviews on different online platforms<br>\u2022 The team size and global presence<br>\u2022 Communication standards<br>\u2022 Customer service standards<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>When looking for the best partner, choose Verv Company. The company believes in offering the best end-to-end solutions to address issues in your company. The team at Verv understands all requirements and thrives on producing the best software while maintaining the company&#8217;s integrity.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"4-start-the-development-process\"><\/span>4. Start the Development Process<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>After deciding on the best company to develop the software, sign a non-disclosure agreement. This agreement ensures that the proprietary information shared remains safe. This step may be the longest; hence you will need to invest more time and resources before it is finalized.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>As the business manager, you need to meet with the development company to ensure that everything runs efficiently. During this stage, ensure that all components such as wireframes and architecture align with the plan.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Once the system is complete and ready, it moves to the testing phase. The testing involves functional and non-functional testing and is achievable automatically or manually. The testing is done to check the following:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u2022 Core application functions<br>\u2022 Software security<br>\u2022 Text input<br>\u2022 Installation process<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The testing process checks for bugs and errors. When detected, the team fixes it and retests it. The process continues until the software performance meets the original requirements.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"5-software-launching-and-maintenance\"><\/span>5. Software Launching and Maintenance<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Your team needs to start getting used to the new software. Therefore, the development company will train the users to use the new application. You may install the program inside the existing system with guidance from the software company. The team will learn how to operate it in conjunction with integrating existing systems.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>After some time, the system may require updates to improve service delivery. Most software development companies offer this service as part of the original package.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"what-are-the-methodologies-used-to-create-customized-apps\"><\/span>What are the Methodologies Used to Create Customized Apps<span class=\"ez-toc-section-e